Nega-Psychic
A rare human whose mind generates a field that suppresses psionic and magical
energies. Nega-Psychics are invisible to many supernatural senses and are a
nightmare for spellcasters and psychics who rely on ambient power.

Starting skills: Detect ambush, intelligence, lore magic, lore psychic,
meditation, streetwise, plus elective picks from Technical, Espionage, and
Physical categories.

Attribute requirements: ME 14.
Starting equipment: Normal clothing, personal sidearm, and little else beyond
a burning desire to be left alone by the supernatural.
Starting credits: 500 credits (standard kit).
PPE / ISP: No starting PPE or ISP. The negation field is innate, not powered.

